A masked surgeon in traditional white garments stands in a misty bamboo forest, holding a gleaming surgical scalpel that catches soft golden light, the blade reflecting both a yin-yang symbol and swirling shadows, their eyes conveying both intensity and compassion above the mask, delicate cherry blossom petals drifting through the air around them, the scene balanced between threat and healing, Eastern and Western aesthetics merging in the composition, rendered in Studio Ghibli animation style with soft watercolor textures, warm amber and cool teal color palette, dreamlike atmosphere with subtle fog weaving between bamboo stalks
